summary: my thoughts on aggretsuko so far: i love retsuko with all my heart and soul  ms. washimi helping retsuko out with her shitty...
body:
my thoughts on aggretsuko so far:

  • i love retsuko with all my heart and soul
  • ms. washimi helping retsuko out with her shitty boss? amazing. brilliant. i love bird woman
  • director gori owns my soul
  • fenneko is best girl
  • pig boss can choke tbh
  • retsuko screaming into the mic during karaoke w/ gori and washimi dancing in the background
  • fenneko joining in on retsuko’s rage modes on the guitar
  • the fact that retsuko can’t leave a store without feeling guilty because she didn’t buy anything w o w  i feel this hard
  • gori and washimi looking out for retsuko and her becoming stronger because of them i’m crying real tears
  • HAIDA
  • tsunoda: i know ppl hate me because i suck up to the boss
  • tsunoda: it’s cool tho idc
  • retsuko screaming about the fact that all she does is go to work and then goes to bed is a perfect summary of my entire life
  • RETSUKO OWNING HER BOSS DURING THE DRINKING PARTY
  • in this house we stan one death metal panda

summary: Was only a matter of time before i got around to these two, based on the cooperative hunting that have been documented between...
caption: Was only a matter of time before i got around to these two, based on the cooperative hunting that have been documented between American badgers and coyotes in the west, in which coyotes will track down and chase prairie dogs into their burrows, where the badger will than pursue the animals. Either the badger will catch them underground or chase them back out into the coyotes jowls.
